title: A Ridiculous Reality (Jabin Chavez)
description: Do something ridiculous and you may just see God do something miraculous. In “A Ridiculous Reality,” Pastor Jabin Chavez of City Light Church challenges us to choose courage over worry and to boldly live out God’s calling on our lives.
